name: Hatched Forms Tigris Moon
description:
Harness the power of the Tiger Moon.

This is a special edition created for the Tezos x Instinc 'TrIGgER' event, a synchronized drop of curated artists from Asia in celebration of the year of the tiger.

Part of a study of creating a simulated plotted ink on paper look through an algorithm which generates hatched lines within custom polygons.

2000 × 2000 GIF, 8 frames
Made in p5js
Created 26 Jan 22

Artist: @Yazid
